<h3>Step 2: Research Your Audience</h3>
<p>Talk to real customers. Review support tickets. Analyze sales calls. Survey your email list. Build 2-3 detailed personas that include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Job title and responsibilities</li>
<li>Key challenges and pain points</li>
<li>Where they search for information</li>
<li>What content formats they prefer</li>
<li>What objections they raise during sales</li>
</ul>
