<h2>How to Build a Content Plan</h2>
<p>Once the strategy is documented, create a plan that executes it.</p>
<h3>Step 1: Map Topics to Pillars</h3>
<p>Generate specific topics for each pillar. A pillar like "SEO and organic growth" produces topics like:</p>
<ul>
<li>How to Conduct a Technical SEO Audit</li>
<li>Keyword Research for B2B SaaS</li>
<li>Building Topic Clusters That Rank</li>
<li>Measuring SEO ROI: A Complete Guide</li>
</ul>
<p>Each topic should target a specific keyword and search intent.</p>
